adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Spirit Temple...^$3Jabu-Jabu's Belly...^$4Forest Temple...^$5Deku Tree...^$6Link's Pocket...^$7Shadow Temple...^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to find %gGreg%w.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will be&provided by Zelda once %r5&Spiritual Stones and Medallions%w&are retrieved.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonText: What about Zelda makes you think&she'd be a better ruler than I?^I saved Lon Lon Ranch,&fed the hungry,&and my castle floats.
ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me&by reflecting my lightning bolts&and unleashing the arrows from&%rDeath Mountain Trail%w!^And even if you do, you'll never&find the legendary blade hidden in&%rDodongo's Cavern%w!
sheikText: I overheard Ganondorf say that he&misplaced the %yLight Arrows%w in&%rDeath Mountain Trail%w.^He also stole %gthe Master Sword%w&and hid it in %rDodongo's&Cavern%w.
dampeText: Whoever reads this, please enter&%rFire Temple%w. I will let you&have my stretching, shrinking&keepsake.^I'm waiting for you.&--Damp√©
